<p>Special thanks go to <a href="http://siobhanmckeown.com/">Siobhan McKeown</a> for producing the release video and <a href="https://jacklenox.com">Jack Lenox</a>Â for the voice-over.</p>
<p>Finally, thanks to all of the contributors who provided translations for the release. WordPress 4.5 comes fully translated into 44 languages and the release video has been translated into 32 languages!</p>
<p>If you want to follow along or help out, check out <a href="https://make.wordpress.org/">Make WordPress</a> and our <a href="https://make.wordpress.org/core/">core development blog</a>. Thanks for choosing WordPress. See you soon for version 4.6!</p>
